CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784812719
OL,3,CGrooming victim makes history after
OL,4,Cconviction quashed
OL,6,FAt the time of her convictions, the
OL,7,FNorth West teenager considered herself
OL,8,Fto be "in a relationship" with a man
OL,9,Fshe had met when she was just 11-years-
OL,10,Fold.
OL,12,FBut despite authorities knowing about
OL,13,Fthe relationship she was treated as a
OL,14,Fperpetrator, and tried in court.
OL,16,FNow her convictions have been
OL,17,Foverturned after a Criminal Cases
OL,18,FReview Commission report found there
OL,19,Fwas "clear evidence" she was a victim
OL,20,Fof grooming and exploitation.
OL,26,@pD@GOUpD@YO]{D@EOU{D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784812719
OL,3,CGrooming victim makes history after
OL,4,Cconviction quashed
OL,6,FSpeaking exclusively to Granada
OL,7,FReports, Ava said: "Growing up I'd
OL,8,Fnever had anybody that really provided
OL,9,Fthe basic needs of things anyway, not
OL,10,Feven my own parents.
OL,12,F"So he definitely made me feel loved
OL,13,Fand cared for and that I had somebody
OL,14,Fwho was my safe space, let's call it
OL,15,Fthat - at that time that was how I
OL,16,Flooked at it."
OL,26,@oD@TOUtD@AOUxD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
