CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784812719
OL,3,CGrooming victim makes history after
OL,4,Cconviction quashed
OL,6,FAt the time Ava's relationship with
OL,7,Fthe man was described in one multi-
OL,8,Fagency referral form as being
OL,9,F"besotted" and open to a large degree
OL,10,Fof manipulation.
OL,12,FShe also disappeared from the care
OL,13,Fhome frequently to spend time with him
OL,14,Fand his friends.
OL,16,FAlongside a number of other offences
OL,17,Fshe was convicted of possessing an
OL,18,Fimitation firearm with intent to cause
OL,19,Ffear of violence. An item that she
OL,20,Fsays did not even belong to her.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784812719
OL,3,CGrooming victim makes history after
OL,4,Cconviction quashed
OL,6,F"There was an altercation one day,"
OL,7,Fshe recalled.
OL,9,F"It came from something really minor,
OL,10,Factually.
OL,12,F"Somebody was assaulted, it kind of
OL,13,Fall got out of hand really quickly,
OL,14,Factually.
OL,16,F"And then I was passed a firearm - to
OL,17,Fthis day I don't know if it was real
OL,18,For if it was fake. I don't know, it
OL,19,Fwas never found by police.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@cO]qD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784812719
OL,3,CGrooming victim makes history after
OL,4,Cconviction quashed
OL,6,F"Nobody ever saw it apart from who was
OL,7,Fthere at the time.
OL,9,F"I'd messed around with it, pulled it
OL,10,Fout, saying 'haha, I'll shoot you'. I
OL,11,Fwas just a kid that thought it was a
OL,12,Fjoke.
OL,14,F"It was only when I heard the police
OL,15,Fsirens, I think I understood the
OL,16,Fseverity of what we'd just done."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUvD@AOUxD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
